datasauRus::datasaurus_dozen %>% 
  ggplot() + 
  aes(x = x, 
      y = y) + 
  geom_point() + 
  facet_wrap(facets = vars(dataset)) + 
  # mean of x
  ggxmean::geom_x_mean() + 
  ggxmean::geom_y_mean() + 
  # mean of y
  ggxmean:::geom_x1sd(linetype = "dashed") + 
  ggxmean:::geom_y1sd(linetype = "dashed") + 
  # linear model
  ggxmean::geom_lm() + 
  ggxmean::geom_lm_formula() + 
  # Pearson correlation
  ggxmean:::geom_corrlabel()
